## Security Checklist

- ✅ Use strong passwords (8+ chars, mixed case, numbers)
- ✅ Enable SSL/HTTPS
- ✅ Use CSRF protection
- ✅ Sanitize user input
- ✅ Use strong parameters
- ✅ Keep secrets secure
- ✅ Update dependencies regularly
- ✅ Use security headers
- ✅ Implement rate limiting
- ✅ Enable authentication
- ✅ Validate authorization
- ✅ Log security events

